# Frontend Flutter

- Share form/grid metadata contract with Angular via the same backend schema.
- Dynamic renderers only — no hard-coded entity screens.
- `flutter analyze` runs in CI (`client-lint-mobile` job).
- Target ≥80% unit test coverage.
